title: Topic 006 Question 019
body: You have a Teams Phone deployment.
When you review the Server - Client summary reports in Teams, you discover that Wired Inside data is unavailable as shown in the following exhibit.
You need to review the monthly and daily trends in the reports.
options: From the Microsoft Teams admin center, configure the network topology.
From the Microsoft Call Quality Dashboard, upload the Building data file.
From the Microsoft Teams admin center, upload reporting labels.
From the Microsoft Call Quality Dashboard, upload the Endpoint data file.
